004package test;
005
006import mkt.Volumes;
007import extDb.CosTb;
008import kut.*;
009import main.Cts;
010
011/** Test volumes. */
012public class J03volume {
013  /**
014  Run test.
015  @param rq Request.
016  @return <pre>
017    {
018      vol: [i.]
019    }
020    </pre>
021  */
022  public static Dic<String> run (Dic<String> rq) {
023    return Dic.mk(
024      "vol", Arr.toJs(Arr.map(
025        Volumes.read(Cts.quotesPath, 60, CosTb.read()),
026        (n) -> (int)(double)n
027        ), Js::w)
028    );
029  }
030
031}
